      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Model input uncertainty assessment is scoped out at MRL 2. Key inputs (viscosity, density, pump geometry dimensions) are sourced from calibrated measurements with documented uncertainty; nominal values used in the simulation are within the measured ranges. Formal probabilistic input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2."
    },
