      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample assessment is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA benchmark dataset used for validation was collected on three nominally identical pump specimens; inter-specimen variability was reported as less than 5% for NIH, which is acceptable for MRL 2 validation purposes. Formal statistical sample size analysis is not required at MRL 2."
